data.description: Experience the feeling of the days stress melting away as your enter this tranquil home, whose attention to detail is breathtaking. Attention Vets. This home has an assumable VA loan for a huge savings potential. Welcome to a home that you can truly just move in and start living the Florida lifestyle, that is immaculate in every way. Upgrades and decor provide a luxury home experience. This single-family Splendor II home features 2 bedrooms, 2 baths with a flex space separated from the main living area that can be an office, den, exercise room, additional guest sleeping area or anything your imagination can conjure up. The kitchen has a great layout upgraded from the builder standard stainless-steel appliances. There is a walk-in pantry with a wood shelving system and motion detection lighting, all for better use of the space. Under-cabinet lighting, a custom show-stopping backsplash, added pendant lighting and a large island. 42” upper cabinets with quartz countertops complete the picture. The washer and dryer in a true laundry room are upgraded as well. Beautiful lighting and ceiling fans throughout with style and efficiency in mind. Flooring is a tasteful plank tile in all common and wet areas. Bedrooms and closets feature plush carpeting. Did I mention the closet system and chandelier in the primary walk-in closet? Primary bath features a double vanity, large walk-in shower and water closet. Quartz countertops here too. The 180 sq ft covered lanai has been screened in for bug free entertainment. Incredible custom window treatments and muted color pallet completes the clean modern feel of this home. The garage offers 2 spaces with additional area to assist with storage or even golf cart parking, The garage even offers storage solutions and added outlets for all of your hobbies. Medley is part of the Mirada community offering the nation’s largest man-made recreational lagoon, at 15 acres. Medley boasts its own private amenity center with a resort style pool, pool bar, café, 24/7 fitness center. There are also card, billiard, yoga and banquet rooms, as well as, pickleball, tennis, shuffle board and bocce courts. Be sure to notice the pet park, and tot-lot for when the grandkids visit. There is even an indoor pet washing station!  Through your HOA fees, residents can use the Crystal Lagoon at no additional charge and comes with 25 free guest passes per year and then extremely reduced admission after the free passes are exhausted. Golf Cart friendly and so many activities within the community it is impossible not to make friends.
